| POP3          | 110         | Post Office Protocol v3 (email)                   |
| NNTP          | 119         | Network News Transfer Protocol                    |
| NTP           | 123         | Network Time Protocol (TCP optional)              |
| IMAP          | 143         | Internet Message Access Protocol                  |
